            { id: 47, title: "Don Quixote", author: "Miguel Cervantes", genre: "Badiiy", year: 1605, lang: "Ingliz", format: "EPUB", rating: 4.7, pages: 900, content: "Don Quixote - idealistik ritsar va uning sadoqatli xizmatkori Sancho Pansaning sarguzashtlari. Haqiqat va xayol o'rtasidagi chegarani ko'rsatuvchi buyuk asar." },
